POE-Component-SSLify version 0.03
=================================

This module makes Net::SSLeay's SSL sockets behave with POE :)

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

	Net::SSLeay

